channel.title: Need help on how to make my server online!?
channel.description:
Hi people,
Me and my friends have recently made an rsps but we are that stupid that we don't how to make it online, well we are having troubles with it. We have watched youtube videos on how to do it but it is being a bit hard to work with. So we have made a host off no-ip.com and now all we need its to know where to put the no-ip address that we made, we went to client.java and typed in server= and put the address there and compiled it didnt work, then we did it to all the client.java's and still didn't work so someone plz help me!!!
It would be easier if someone could do it for me, you can do that by downloading Teamviewer6-this prog allows you to view other peoples screen but only with there user and pass. Plz reply, pm me, or email me-Race.fox@hotmail.com
